  "primaryContentSections": [
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "overview",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Capabilities simplify the configuration process for many of Apple’s services,",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "some of which require you to configure specific entitlements or change your",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "app’s provisioning profile. When you add a capability to an app or other target",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "in your project, Xcode automatically configures that target to use the",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "corresponding service. For example, Xcode might add a required entitlement to",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "a new entitlements file and configure the project to use those entitlements.",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "When Xcode needs you to provide additional information, it presents a",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "simplified UI for you to specify that information.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "identifier": "capabilities",
              "type": "image"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "content": [
            {
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "text": "You add most capabilities directly from Xcode, but some app services —",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": " ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": "such as Game Center and In-App Purchase — require additional setup in App Store",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": " ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": "Connect and your developer account. For more information, see the documentation",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": " ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": "below for the specific capability.",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ],
              "type": "paragraph"
            }
          ],
          "name": "Note",
          "style": "note",
          "type": "aside"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
  ],
